speco.set

Interface MultiSet<K,V>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<V>, java.lang.Iterable<V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayMultiSet, ListMultiSet

    public interface MultiSet<K,V>
extends Collection<V>

    Title: MultiSet

    Description: A set allowing multiple copies of an element. Provide access to elements using an index/key.
